metadata.name: dw. Aiuso Yakyo
metadata.description:
Aiuso Yakyo, a work of art  
That makes one question, from the start  
Do we make architecture with nature or nature with architecture?  
A blend or a monument, which is the feature?

This piece speaks of a dream dwelling  
Overfilled and overtaken by nature's swelling  
Is it the intention or just a result  
Of nature winning over man's adult?

The viewer must decide or the creator allow  
For coexistence and correlation to always avow  
Aiuso Yakyo, a monument or blend  
Nature and architecture until the very end.
